{"data":[{"id":563784348,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"159de35381ffa57ff35dbdd4da99a2d1","url_token":"li-gou-bu-hai","name":"德拉根宝","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-348cc58edb5a7c2690bc1a1aa152f5be_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-348cc58edb5a7c2690bc1a1aa152f5be_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/159de35381ffa57ff35dbdd4da99a2d1","user_type":"people","headline":"进阶法律人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":2,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563784348","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9f2a3cb17817b87ee9fc471f2957fc30_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546276633,"updated_time":1546312099,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":16,"comment_count":7,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e2019.1.1 11.02编辑\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他删文章了。据他所说，他“曾经我一度觉得自己证明出了这一猜想”，算是委婉承认自己错了？于是证明同学现在正表现出努力销号的样子给我们看。也许是为了躲些砖头，也许是接着炒冷饭。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e似乎有点失落啊，对于他，对于吃瓜的我们。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17226e2b488030a16ab781baa4692342_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"713\" data-rawheight=\"596\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-385f79c13407271a04c5a9e5de907f20_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"713\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17226e2b488030a16ab781baa4692342_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='713'%20height='596'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"713\" data-rawheight=\"596\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-385f79c13407271a04c5a9e5de907f20_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"713\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17226e2b488030a16ab781baa4692342_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17226e2b488030a16ab781baa4692342_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e他要是继续荡着，坚持不懈地说自己是对的，也许还是会有一群吃瓜群众给他赞给他好评呢，现在不还有3万多关注嘛。明明还可以自媒体再来一波，说不定可以身跻郭英森行列呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这么认怂，没意思呀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过我也不想评论他了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在这新年第一天，我们看到了不少人心甘情愿为他造势起哄，心甘情愿被耍，心甘情愿被带节奏（也许证明出了呢），一起演同一场戏。好在这也就是一个无关紧要的提问而已，看了就看了，骗了就骗了嘛。只是，是不是还有其他类似的事情，在紧要的领域发生着呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过也有好的一面吧，这一次，朋友们应该认识到了，为什么那些知名学者教授不愿意以善意来面对这些“潜在的科学家”了。累。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下为原回答。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e刚刚见到该高中生的回答了。我不知道内容正确与否，但我看到了一大堆人无视严谨科学正确与否直接给赞，才一个小时就为 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 积累了2000余赞，6000余评论。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只看到了全民跨年的狂欢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果说这是对一条评论点赞，可以理解为是对抖机灵开玩笑的赞许；但当这是对一个回答的评价时，抱着“厉害了”“嘲讽式点赞”的心态点赞，就是对自己点赞价值的侮辱。截至目前的六千多条评论，基本都是“前排”“留名”的评论，见不到几个有价值评论，也足见这种看客心理了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以我认为，“高中生证明哥猜能否保送清北”作为问题来说，回答是能（当然以这位高中生答出来为前提，这一点可以坐等稍后大牛的认真评论）；作为事件，凸显的是知乎对有价值问答的忽视、对这种流量事件的放纵。我的感觉是，流量跟泡沫一样，终将驱逐良币，毁灭市场。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也许这是一种卫道士心理，毕竟大众喜欢啥我管不着吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-687bb0ce41b0ce2e437a5851f6a93813_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2244\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6290a1dd0a21eec796a7d9307d0f886b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-687bb0ce41b0ce2e437a5851f6a93813_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='2244'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2244\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6290a1dd0a21eec796a7d9307d0f886b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-687bb0ce41b0ce2e437a5851f6a93813_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-687bb0ce41b0ce2e437a5851f6a93813_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"2019.1.1 11.02编辑他删文章了。据他所说，他“曾经我一度觉得自己证明出了这一猜想”，算是委婉承认自己错了？于是证明同学现在正表现出努力销号的样子给我们看。也许是为了躲些砖头，也许是接着炒冷饭。似乎有点失落啊，对于他，对于吃瓜的我们。他要是继…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Cconten